data.description: MOVE IN READY! This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and stylish design. Situated in one of South Tampa's most sought after neighborhoods, this home boasts an array of impressive features that will surely captivate your heart and is minutes away from MacDill Air Force base, with easy access to Picnic Island, Downtown Tampa, and the Gandy Bridge that leads to St. Petersburg and the Gulf beaches. Step inside and be greeted by the spacious and inviting living areas, adorned with tasteful finishes and an abundance of natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage space. Prepare delicious meals while enjoying the company of loved ones at the large island or the dining area. The master suite comes complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a large walk-in shower and a custom walk-in closet. The additional three bedrooms offer generous space and comfort for family members or guests. Step outside into your own private oasis. The fenced backyard provides privacy whilst enjoying the Florida sun. Indulge in the backyard bar, perfect for hosting unforgettable gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day. The fresh landscaping adds a touch of beauty and serenity to the outdoor space, creating a picturesque setting for relaxation and entertainment.  Additional features include built-in organizers in the master closet and laundry area, providing efficient storage solutions and streamlining your daily routines. Solar that significantly reduces your energy costs, mosquito and bug sprayer system and a water softener system!   Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers easy access to schools, shopping centers, dining options, and recreational facilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. Schedule your showing Today!!
